 later in 18.303).
 Define the inner product of two vector fields 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{u}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{v}$
\end_inset

 by the volume integral 
\begin_inset Formula $\langle\vec{u},\vec{v}\rangle=\int_{\Omega}\bar{\vec{u}}\cdot\vec{v}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

